40/extras/282a2ed8390cac893ab7457fdb1a17f9.poster.avif?t=1737527172\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1737340/extras/282a2ed8390cac893ab7457fdb1a17f9.webm?t=1737527172\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1737340/extras/282a2ed8390cac893ab7457fdb1a17f9.mp4?t=1737527172\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1737340/extras/b9798490db06c8ff8b24788b006bc3e9.avif?t=1737527172\" width=620 height=80 /></span>Each upgrade may be what takes you from wimp to hero! Spend gold to reroll your skill selections! Oh, and gain meta-progression in the shape of talent points to make your runs easier as you progress!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1737340/extras/8f61e20d7e6ec06a30faea17b8dddabc.poster.avif?t=1737527172\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1737340/extras/8f61e20d7e6ec06a30faea17b8dddabc.webm?t=1737527172\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1737340/extras/8f61e20d7e6ec06a30faea17b8dddabc.mp4?t=1737527172\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1737340/extras/86c20e7ab34abe51b781b4367775806d.avif?t=1737527172\" width=620 height=100 /></span></p>",
